            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1695715707752-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ground paprika</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>mayo </strong>– this is your <strong>paprika mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695715711404-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695715711404-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695715711404-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695715711404-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1695715711404-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper, then remove 1 <strong>whole outer leaf </strong>per person and set aside for serving</p><p>Tear the <strong>remaining lettuce </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>torn lettuce leaves</strong> to a bowl and mix with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1695715719051-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1695715719051-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1695715719051-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1695715719051-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1695715719051-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to a baking tray, cut side up, and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1695715727621-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1695715727621-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1695715727621-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1695715727621-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1695715727621-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger top a <strong>warmed brioche bun base</strong> with some of the <strong>paprika mayo</strong>, a <strong>reserved lettuce leaf</strong>, some of the <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong>, a <strong>peri peri butter bean patty</strong>, the <strong>sliced cheddar </strong>and a<strong> warmed brioche bun lid</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips</strong>, <strong>corn</strong>, <strong>remaining paprika mayo</strong>, <strong>salad </strong>and the <strong>remaining quick</strong>-<strong>pickled red onion </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
